column5: Al organized the 1st of many work bees over the next 3 weeks, 7 Adults & 2 - 6 year old twin girls showed up to start the Counting & Sorting, 19,000 Rainbows down & 50,000? more to go plus the 70,000 Browns are hatched out & doing Great, next Saturday will be the next one. Tight Lines SBK  Counting & Sorting 19,000 Rainbows & 70,000 Brown Hatched
